Description_lang: Increases your maximum Runic Power by ${$s1/10} and increases the Rune regeneration rate of Runic Corruption by $s2%.

description_blz.en_US: Increases your maximum Runic Power by 10 and increases the Rune regeneration rate of Runic Corruption by 10%.
